https://bugs.launchpad.net/heat/+bug/1434427

Docker 1.2.0 and docker-py 0.6.0 support the device parameter when
starting containers(docker run --device[]).

You can adding a host device to the container (e.g. --device=/dev/sdc:/dev/xvdc)
Note:":" is used to split the full device path.
https://github.com/docker/docker-py/blob/master/docker/utils/utils.py#L259 (parse_devices)

https://github.com/docker/docker-py/blob/master/docs/change_log.md
https://docs.docker.com/reference/api/docker_remote_api/

Closes-bug: #1434427
